OL,4,CCitigroup launches Zoom-free Fridays to
OL,5,Cease pandemic 'fatigue'
OL,6, American investment bank Citigroup has
OL,7, urged its staff to limit video calls on
OL,8, Fridays in an effort to promote a
OL,9, better work-life balance.
OL,11,FChief executive Jane Fraser told staff
OL,12,Fto observe "Zoom-free Fridays", in a
OL,13,Fmemo on Monday.
OL,15,FShe also said 28 May would be
OL,16,Fdesignated as a company-wide holiday,
OL,17,Fknown as a "reset day".
OL,19,FMs Fraser used the memo to address how
OL,20,Fworking practices would change when the
OL,21,Fcoronavirus pandemic has passed.
